\begin_inset Formula $\nabla\times\frac{1}{\varepsilon}\nabla\times\vec{H}=\frac{\omega^{2}}{c^{2}}\vec{H}$
\end_inset

.
 Suppose that we replace 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

